Hey Streamlit devs,
 
The latest release is out…and it hits all the right buttons! Check out some new widgets and other helpful updates below. Also, learn about Community Cloud profile pages, building effective AI apps, and connecting with the community.
&#128680;  Release 1.40
Highlights 



	-  &#128138; Introducing st.pills <https://go.snowflake.net/MjUyLVJGTy0yMjcAAAGXA0vfHHm5o1kvEjEuhHM4d7MRw6Wnfqp0fKZgt_7ND7pOqftLG4wuoqxRGI4RgpbGUx1_HVs=> to create a single- or multi-select group of pill-buttons.
	- &#127899; Introducing st.segmented_control <https://go.snowflake.net/MjUyLVJGTy0yMjcAAAGXA0vfHGvjKW5evqBTbBlwcJpERRqYD2jJqRPyCIQftA_HPSu8N2ZXA9z1T31txsLImUZfDHw=> to create a segmented button or button group.
	- &#127908; Now generally available, st.audio_input <https://go.snowflake.net/MjUyLVJGTy0yMjcAAAGXA0vfHBafY323Scbmxa0Oe3dKy_N-htK4G8Rs0tuJJXNPM1thCPzwXfCvCBAUzWsWff7BpL8=> to record sound with microphones.
	- &#10145; Markdown renders a limited set of typographical symbols (arrows and comparators).
	- &#127880; You can use :streamlit: to render the Streamlit logo in Markdown.


See the full changelog <https://go.snowflake.net/MjUyLVJGTy0yMjcAAAGXA0vfHHz_i1QfGLgiMZyPJ400_oCdfN7l0DdEHzL5B07FB2NywY18tBE0C32FwK0J_BqZYCA=> and download the latest version of Streamlit.
&#128161; Share your work with profile pages
Announcing profile pages on Community Cloud! You can now showcase all your creations in a shareable, discoverable profile. Feature your favorite app, display total app views, add a personalized bio, and more. Learn more here. <https://go.snowflake.net/MjUyLVJGTy0yMjcAAAGXA0vfHExMqH2osN2xAPVzLDSP8NnZfwuP-rkIsDMSYGENckR4sLTo_Zilc2n6czByFBo5lj4=>
&#128640; Build AI-powered apps with TruLens
TruLens helps measure and improve LLM-based apps with feedback functions, enabling you to assess inputs, outputs, and results more effectively. This is useful for tasks like question answering, summarization, and retrieval-augmented generation! See how to combine it with Streamlit in this demo <https://go.snowflake.net/MjUyLVJGTy0yMjcAAAGXA0vfHOV1JoYd24vGkpdcXOyky-idPqB3utK-DqPUzYOIZHNMjotsK9H42udQDJ_pSXzMyBM=> from Josh and Chanin.
